name: SRNGen
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Page of SRNGen.
SCEL presents **Sudo Random Number generator**, lightweight solution using c++/CLI for windows desktop environment.

### Releases
v0.1 released for x_86 and x_64 based pc.

### Upgrades
* Modern UI
* Multiple Random number Generation
* Save to .txt option
* Option to choose between different method for Random number generation

### Authors and Contributors
Purnendu Kumar @PurnenduK90 for @SCE-Labs 

### Support or Contact
If you want any specific update please mail to scel@satakshi.in or satakshi.india@gmail.com
For bugs, raise issue in Githud, although you can mail also, but it is less reliable and may take time.
